articles.author: Jon Haworth
articles.title: 12-year-old missing after being attacked and taken by crocodile: Report - ABC News
articles.description: The incident occurred in a remote town called Palumpa in Australia.
articles.content:
LONDON -- Police in Australia have launched a search near a remote community for a missing 12-year-old after reports that they were attacked and taken by a crocodile while swimming in a creek.
